<tr id="L355"><td><a href="#L355">355</a></td><td>PICARD:  Rishon, I can touch you. I can hear your voice, I can smell your perfume. In every respect you are a real person with your own mind and beliefs, but you do not exist. You died along with the others, defending the colony. He recreated you, just as he recreated the house.</td></tr>

